            <title><![CDATA[【孕期吃素，3个月喂粥，6岁娃比平均身高矮17cm[衰]】“已经达到矮小，而且比矮小还矮！”“孕期吃素你不觉得有很大问题吗？” 诊室里，医生眉头紧锁，声音里夹...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【孕期吃素，3个月喂粥，6岁娃比平均身高矮17cm<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[衰]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shuai-285d2d97c7.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】“已经达到矮小，而且比矮小还矮！”<br>“孕期吃素你不觉得有很大问题吗？” 诊室里，医生眉头紧锁，声音里夹杂着轻微怒火。6岁3个月的娃，身高102cm，远低于同龄人平均水平119cm，预测孩子成年身高仅150cm。细问才知，妈妈不仅孕期吃素，更是以“吃母乳上火”为由，给3个月大的娃喂米粥当正餐。当医生建议打生长激素，妈妈一再纠结激素的负影响。以父母身高预估，若孩子低于生长水平线，应尽早带去医院内分泌科就诊。（拍摄已签署授权书）<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%97%AA%E9%97%AA%E7%9A%84%E5%84%BF%E7%A7%91%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%97%AA%E9%97%AA%E7%9A%84%E5%84%BF%E7%A7%91%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#闪闪的儿科医生#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%AD%95%E6%9C%9F%E5%90%83%E7%B4%A0%E8%87%B46%E5%B2%81%E5%A8%83%E6%AF%94%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E8%BA%AB%E9%AB%98%E7%9F%AE17cm%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%AD%95%E6%9C%9F%E5%90%83%E7%B4%A0%E8%87%B46%E5%B2%81%E5%A8%83%E6%AF%94%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E8%BA%AB%E9%AB%98%E7%9F%AE17cm%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#孕期吃素致6岁娃比平均身高矮17cm#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4905328928555017" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">深圳卫健委的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/a8bfee30gy1hear22dzuzj21hc0u07g5.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/NaWhN8z3gx085IukYHEQ01041200qgLu0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1685049372&amp;ssig=0WxjCDynOH&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/O0N2E4h1gx085IukpWIg01041200dSBk0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;o